      <title>加拿大的眼睛北极军事扩张，以应对特朗普的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/canada-eyes-arctic-military-expansion-in-response-to-trump-s-demands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大试图安抚特朗普政府要求更高国防支出的呼吁，并阻止中国和俄罗斯在偏远地区的影响力，从而扩大了其在北极地区的军事存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/canada-eyes-arctic-military-expansion-in-response-to-trump-s-demands</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 16:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC的Uyeda预计“雄心勃勃”拜登时代的规则制定会放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/sec-s-uyeda-expects-slowdown-in-rulemaking-after-ambitious-biden-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会的临时负责人说，他预计在经过三年半的“过于雄心勃勃”的市场改革之后，华尔街监管机构的规则制定会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/sec-s-uyeda-expects-slowdown-in-rulemaking-after-ambitious-biden-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 16:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
