    <item>
      <title>Scope说，德国债务可能会在五年内增加6250亿欧元。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/german-debt-may-swell-by-625-billion-in-five-years-scope-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据Scope Ratings的数据，德国的借款可能会在未来五十年内激起多达13％的国内生产总值，以资助其计划在国防和基础设施上的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/german-debt-may-swell-by-625-billion-in-five-years-scope-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 16:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦与削减欧洲央行率抗衡货币钉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/denmark-matches-ecb-rate-cut-to-defend-currency-peg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦的中央银行将其基准率降低了四分之一点，与欧洲同行保持一致，以捍卫克朗的钉子到欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/denmark-matches-ecb-rate-cut-to-defend-currency-peg</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 16:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在LBO债务出售中，咨询公司BRG遭受网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/consulting-firm-brg-suffers-cyberattack-amid-debt-sale-for-lbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解此事的人说，伯克利研究小组上周遭受了网络攻击，就像银行一直在寻求结束债务出售，这将为塔尔布鲁克资本合作伙伴的咨询公司的买断提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/consulting-firm-brg-suffers-cyberattack-amid-debt-sale-for-lbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克（Lutnick）发出信号特朗普可能会退缩关税时，石油会波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如美国商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）一样，石油在收益和损失之间倾斜，继续进行一系列动荡的会议，特朗普政府可能会减轻对该国两个最大贸易伙伴的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
